[src:soda-data-quality/docs-soda-io] Full control over orchestration, in-memory data support, contract verification.
[src:soda-data-quality/docs-soda-io] Managed version of Soda that runs observability features, executes Data Contracts and scheduled them.
[src:soda-data-quality/docs-soda-io] Teams seeking a simple, managed solution for data quality.
[src:soda-data-quality/docs-soda-io] Centralized data source access, no setup required, observability features enabled.
