[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] A test script is a procedure or programming code that replicates user actions.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] Initially, the term was derived from the product of work created by automated regression test tools.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] A test case will be a baseline to create test scripts using a tool or a program.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] In software development, a test suite, less commonly known as a validation suite, is a collection of test cases that are intended to be used to test a software program to show that it has some specified set of behaviors.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] A test suite often contains detailed instructions or goals for each collection of test cases and information on the system configuration to be used during testing.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] A group of test cases may also contain prerequisite states or steps and descriptions of the following tests.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] In most cases, multiple sets of values or data are used to test the same functionality of a particular feature.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] All the test values and changeable environmental components are collected in separate files and stored as test data.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] It is also useful to provide this data to the client and with the product or a project.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] There are techniques to generate Test data.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] The software, tools, samples of data input and output, and configurations are all referred to collectively as a test harness.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] A test run is a collection of test cases or test suites that the user is executing and comparing the expected with the actual results.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] Once complete, a report or all executed tests may be generated.
[src:soda-data-quality/software-testing-p02] Several certification programs exist to support the professional aspirations of software testers and quality assurance specialists.
